> +	 *	in a reserved page - free, assume the pointer was
> +	 *	    acquired with malloc, since it couldn't have been kmalloced.
>  	 * 	physical memory - kmalloc/kfree
>  	 *	kernel virtual memory - vmalloc/vfree
>  	 * 	anywhere else - malloc/free
